    "description": "LIKE, Inc. provides human resource services in Japan. It operates through Comprehensive Human Resources Service, Child-Rearing Support Service, and Nursing Care-Related Service segments. The company offers human resource services comprising temporary staffing, outsourcing, recruitment, placement, and hiring and education support services. It also operates on-site childcare facilities, licensed nurseries, after-school clubs, and other public childcare facilities that offer outsourced and public childcare services. In addition, the company operates nursing homes that offer nursing and elderly care services. LIKE, Inc. was formerly known as J-COM Holdings Co., Ltd. and changed its name to LIKE, Inc. in December 2016. LIKE, Inc. was incorporated in 1993 and is based in Osaka, Japan."
